1015
01:24:32,268 --> 01:24:34,429
Sung-ju! Ada apa?

1016
01:24:35,271 --> 01:24:38,331
- Gucinya..
- Gucimu?

1017
01:25:27,290 --> 01:25:30,418
Jangan lewat waktu.

1018
01:25:32,328 --> 01:25:34,421
Dong-yeon!

1019
01:25:36,299 --> 01:25:38,494
Won Dong-yeon!

