- Ya, kawan, apa kabar?

1021
01:25:49,512 --> 01:25:51,377
Apa ini mimpi?

1022
01:25:51,414 --> 01:25:53,211
Ya.

1023
01:25:53,249 --> 01:25:54,375
Aku bisa melihatmu di mimpi.

1024
01:25:54,417 --> 01:25:56,510
