01:28:50,359 --> 01:28:52,486
Jangan pernah menyia-nyiakan..

1066
01:28:52,495 --> 01:29:00,493
air mata yang baru di masa lalu..

1067
01:29:00,503 --> 01:29:04,496
Sobat, mengapa kau mengatakan itu?

1068
01:29:04,540 --> 01:29:11,241
