1069
01:29:12,348 --> 01:29:13,315
Hei, kemarilah.

1070
01:29:13,316 --> 01:29:15,341
Kim, berhenti!

1071
01:29:24,393 --> 01:29:26,258
Apa?

1072
01:29:33,502 --> 01:29:35,333
Ada apa?

1073
01:29:35,371 --> 01:29:38,340
